results.title: Avengers (1998) #17
results.description: A team of Avengers pursues the Wrecking Crew, which has abducted Photon to another realm, while the rest of Earth's Mightiest Heroes must save Carol Danvers from the Doomsday Man.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #18
results.description: The Avengers join forces with Thundra and her people to help overthrow the Wrecking Crew, who've taken over Arkon's realm by siphoning energy from Photon.

results.title: Avengers (1998) #19
results.description: Following the kidnapping of Hank Pym, the Avengers head to Wakanda where they face a most formidable foe: Alkhema, the bride of Ultron!

results.title: Avengers (1998) #23
results.description: Amidst public outcry for a more racially diverse team of Avengers, the Vision confronts Wonder Man about the unusual connection that they share.
